PF4 (MINOR): R3's CI-job placement latitude ("addition to the existing docs workflow or a sibling workflow") is preserved. Recommended placement: add a step to the existing `build` job in `.github/workflows/docs.yaml` after the `uv sync` step, reusing the uv cache. A parallel job would also work but adds a cold-start cost for a ~second-scale script. Not blocking; decision deferred to build phase.

